overview: Wicked Pictures and Director Jim Enright team up to bring you this classic tale. Girl meets girl. Girl eats girl. Several friends show up. Everyone collapses in a heap. Who could ask for more? This all-girl Extravaganza, with a touch of the macabre will have you squirming on your Ouija Board. Yes Jennifer, dreams do come true. Bon Appetit. Enjoy this great title from Wicked Pictures!
title: Jennifer Ate
